<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
	<meta charset="UTF-8">
	<title>URLittle</title>

	<link rel="stylesheet" href="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/3.3.6/css/bootstrap.min.css">
</head>
<body>
	<h1 class="text-center"> Timestamp Microservice API </h1>

	<h3 class="text-center"> FreeCodeCamp Basejump </h3>

	<div class="container">
		<blockquote>
			<h4>User stories</h4>
			<ul>
				<li>I can pass a URL as a parameter and I will receive a shortened URL in the JSON reponse.</li>
				<li>When I visit that shortened URL, it will redirect me to my orginal link</li>
			</ul>
		</blockquote>

		<h2>Example creation usage:</h2>
		<code>https://URLittle.herokuapp.com/new/www.google.com</code><br>
		<code>https://URLittle.herokuapp.com/new/foo.com:80</code>

		<h2> Example creation output </h2>
		<code>{ "original_url":"http://foo.com:80", "short_url":"https://urlittle.herokuapp.com/short/ened/8170" }</code>

		<h2> Usage: </h2>
		<code>https://urlittle.herokuapp.com/short/ened/2871</code> <span>Redirects to: </span><code>https://www.google.com/</code>
	</div>
	
</body>
</html>